  TaN chit-e5 thau5-ke-niu5 mi5-jit8 su-liam7, ai3 siN chit8-e5 eN-a2. ¡§Goa2 liam-piN beh u7 gin2-na2 lah!¡¨ Thau5-ke-niu5 ka7 i chhin-bit8 e5 chhu3-piN kong2. I ia7 siong-sin3 i beh u7 gin2-na2. Chiu7 mi5-jit8 to2 chhng5. ¡§Lan2 e5 siu-jip8 siuN-chio2, gin2-na2 na7 chhut-si3 beh an2-choaN2 seng-oah8!¡¨ Thau5-ke niu5 tioh8 tui3 A-peh an2-ni kong2, m7-si7 kong2, si7 an2-ni jiong2 lai5 ui-hat i. Chong2-si7 A-peh e5 sim-lai7 teh chhio3, ¡§Hi, hi, li2 beh siN chit8-e5 kui2 lah!¡¨ 
